      "writtenOn": "2020-01-30T04:01:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "When we’re in the Chromium tree, you’re going to want to pick up Chromium’s copy of edo, not this, which won’t even be available. (When checking out Chromium, we don’t recurse into Crashpad’s DEPS file.)\n\nThere’s precedent for handling this situation. See third_party/zlib/BUILD.gn, for example.\n\nIt’s not necessary that you handle this now, but I’m pointing it out so that you can be aware that it’ll need to happen before any of this works in Chromium.",
